b4w_object_tags.title: 1. Plug in the charger
b4w_object_tags.description: Click/tap the charger. Plug in DC for charging, (DC IN 14.8V, 1A)

b4w_object_tags.title: 2.1. Red LED will lights up when charging
b4w_object_tags.description: Indicate ON and OFF (Lights up = ON)

b4w_object_tags.title: 2.2. GreenLED will light up, if such level is charging, it will blink
b4w_object_tags.description: Indicate power level (Higher battery level = more lights on, max = 4 lights on)
